<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Index Page</title>
    <style>
        /* Reset and Base Styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            color: #333;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        a {
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Navbar Styles */
        .navbar {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #833ab4, #fd1d1d, #fcb045);
            color: white;
            padding: 20px 40px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .navbar .logo {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: white;
        }
        .navbar a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .navbar a:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .navbar a:active {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #fcb045, #fd1d1d, #833ab4);
            color: white;
            padding: 100px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-bottom-left-radius: 50px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 50px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background-color: white;
            color: #fd1d1d;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover {
            background-color: #fd1d1d;
            color: white;
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .btn-primary:active {
            transform: translateY(2px);
            box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        /* About Section */
        .about {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .about h2 {
            color: #833ab4;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .about p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 10px;
        }

        /* Services Section */
        .services {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 6px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .services h2 {
            color: #fd1d1d;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .services .service {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        .service-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 30px;
            max-width: 280px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .service-card:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }
        .service-card h3 {
            color: #833ab4;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
        }
        .service-card p {
            font-size: 1rem;
        }

        /* Testimonials Section */
        .testimonials {
            text-align: center;
            background: #f4f4f4;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }
        .testimonials h2 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .testimonial {
            font-style: italic;
            color: #666;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            max-width: 700px;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .testimonial:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #833ab4, #fd1d1d, #fcb045);
            color: white;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: underline;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            color: #fcb045;
        }

        /* Media Queries */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .navbar {
                padding: 20px 10px;
            }
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2.2rem;
            }
            .hero p {
                font-size: 1.1rem;
            }
            .about h2 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .services .service {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 20px;
            }
            .service-card {
                max-width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="navbar">
        <div class="logo">Index Page</div>
        <div>
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/about">About</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero">
        <h1>Welcome to the Index Page</h1>
        <p>Explore a variety of modern, interactive features designed to elevate your online experience.</p>
        <a href="#about" class="btn-primary">Learn More</a>
    </div>

    <section id="about" class="about">
        <h2>About This Website</h2>
        <p>This is the Index page of a modern website designed to provide a sleek, responsive experience for all users. Our mission is to showcase top-quality web design and innovative solutions to meet your needs.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="services" class="services">
        <h2>Our Featured Services</h2>
        <div class="service">
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>Web Design</h3>
                <p>Beautiful, responsive designs that make your website stand out and perform seamlessly across all devices.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>SEO Optimization</h3>
                <p>Optimize your website to rank higher in search engines, boosting traffic and online visibility.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-card">
                <h3>E-commerce Solutions</h3>
                <p>Build your online store with powerful features to maximize sales and improve customer experience.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="testimonials" class="testimonials">
        <h2>What Our Clients Are Saying</h2>
        <p class="testimonial">"The design of this website is simply amazing. It has completely transformed how we engage with users online!"</p>
        <p class="testimonial">"I can't thank the team enough for the incredible SEO results. Our site now ranks higher than ever before!"</p>
    </section>

    <footer class="footer">
        <p>&copy; 2024 Index Page. All rights reserved. <a href="/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
